STATE v. GILBERT. No. COA06-16. North Carolina Court of Appeals. Filed December 5, 2006. Certification Date December 27, 2006. Appeal from Gaston (04CRS64133, 04CRS18296, 04CRS18297, 04CRS64779, 04CRS26161).

Case reported without published opinion. No error as to trial; vacated in part and remanded for resentencing.
